<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Refund & Cancellation | GardenRich</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-50 font-sans antialiased text-zinc-900">
    <%- include("partials/header") %>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm font-bold text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 mb-4 inline-block">← Back to Home</a>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-2">Refund & Cancellation</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-medium mb-12">Our goal is your 100% satisfaction.</p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 shadow-sm border border-zinc-100 space-y-12">
            
            <section class="border-l-4 border-green-600 pl-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4">Cancellation Policy</h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Orders can be cancelled within 2 hours of placement or before they are shipped, whichever is earlier. Once an order is "Shipped," it cannot be cancelled.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6">Returns & Exchanges</h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    Due to the personal nature of our products (skincare/haircare), we only accept returns if:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 shrink-0"></span>
                        <span class="text-zinc-600 font-medium">The product received is damaged or leaked.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 shrink-0"></span>
                        <span class="text-zinc-600 font-medium">The wrong item was delivered.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 shrink-0"></span>
                        <span class="text-zinc-600 font-medium">The product has passed its expiry date at the time of delivery.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4">Refund Process</h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Approved refunds will be processed within 5-7 business days to the original payment method. For Cash on Delivery (COD) orders, we will request your bank details for a bank transfer.
                </p>
            </section>

        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>